00:25:18.080 --> 00:25:21.860
So give them the final word and maybe offer to pray.

00:25:21.860 --> 00:25:26.420
You were created in his image.

00:25:27.960 --> 00:25:31.640
Who better than he to know what you need to heal?

00:25:31.640 --> 00:25:35.840
So as we move forward,

00:25:35.840 --> 00:25:39.100
I just really encourage people to discern,

00:25:39.100 --> 00:25:41.120
to do those things that bring joy.

00:25:41.120 --> 00:25:43.020
The joy of the Lord is our strength,

00:25:43.020 --> 00:25:45.840
to find that peace that surpasses all understanding.

00:25:45.840 --> 00:25:47.720
And when we get back in touch physically,

00:25:47.720 --> 00:25:51.560
emotionally and spiritually in alignment with him,

00:25:51.560 --> 00:25:55.800
hearing his voice, he is very true to his promises.

00:25:55.800 --> 00:25:56.840
They don't return void.

00:25:56.840 --> 00:26:01.440
He will actually lead us into the steps and the way

00:26:01.440 --> 00:26:06.440
that allows us to experience health, healing and joy,

00:26:06.440 --> 00:26:10.280
regardless of whatever's going on

00:26:10.280 --> 00:26:12.200
in the situation around us.

00:26:12.200 --> 00:26:14.400
Anytime we make decision from fear,

00:26:14.400 --> 00:26:16.740
we're making it from the point of the view of the enemy.

00:26:16.740 --> 00:26:18.240
So what I would like to do now

00:26:18.240 --> 00:26:19.720
is just to pray for everyone.

00:26:19.720 --> 00:26:20.560
Please.

00:26:20.560 --> 00:26:23.960
Lord, we just praise you and thank you

00:26:24.880 --> 00:26:27.160
for the fact that all things work together for good

00:26:27.160 --> 00:26:28.320
for those who love you

00:26:28.320 --> 00:26:30.560
and are called according to your purpose.

00:26:30.560 --> 00:26:34.060
So today we just ask that you reach through

00:26:34.060 --> 00:26:36.000
to every single person

00:26:36.000 --> 00:26:43.500
that they see, hear, feel, and know you.

00:26:43.500 --> 00:26:45.960
Know your voice, Lord.

00:26:45.960 --> 00:26:48.700
If they're in a position of confusion,

00:26:48.700 --> 00:26:51.280
that they will turn to you,

00:26:51.280 --> 00:26:53.060
take that moment to get quiet,

00:26:54.260 --> 00:26:57.060
to ask and feel you, Lord,

00:26:57.060 --> 00:26:58.940
and that you will guide their steps

00:26:58.940 --> 00:27:01.120
in the way that you would have them go,

00:27:01.120 --> 00:27:03.500
that they will no longer give away the autonomy

00:27:03.500 --> 00:27:05.400
over the temple that you've given them,

00:27:05.400 --> 00:27:09.440
but that they will feel the joy and the peace

00:27:09.440 --> 00:27:12.600
of you guiding them through the care of that temple.

00:27:12.600 --> 00:27:15.280
In Jesus' name we pray, amen.

00:27:15.280 --> 00:27:16.220
Amen.

